description: Retrieves a list of vehicle models (model manifests).

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: A pagination token for the next set of results. If the results of a search are large, only a portion of the results are returned, and a nextToken pagination token is returned in the response. To retrieve the next set of results, reissue the search request and include the returned token. When all results have been returned, the response does not contain a pagination token value.

nested_items.name: summaries
nested_items.description: A list of information about vehicle models.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the vehicle model.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the vehicle model.

nested_items.name: signalCatalogArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the signal catalog associated with the vehicle model.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the vehicle model.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The state of the vehicle model. If the status is ACTIVE, the vehicle model can't be edited. If the status is DRAFT, you can edit the vehicle model.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the vehicle model was created, in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).

nested_items.name: lastModificationTime
nested_items.description: The time the vehicle model was last updated, in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to retrieve the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
